        <item>
            <title>Threads 分享真入境處來電慘被 3 次 cut 線，網民回應：經常被當成詐騙電話</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Threads]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[入境處]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[詐騙電話]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268930</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信各位朋友都曾經收過騙徒冒充入境處的詐騙電話，因此大家一接到聲稱來自入境處的來電均會有戒心。早前有網民在 Threads 分享指，友人曾經多次接獲聲稱來自入境處的電話，誤以為是詐騙電話，因此多次收線，直至對方哀求「我求下你唔好收線呀，求下你聽一聽我講先」，再交代來電源由，友人才警醒是真入境處來電。</p><div class="-ml-3 w-screen md:ml-0 md:w-full"><div class="placeholder-hk01"><div class="lazyload-wrapper "></div></div></div><blockquote id="ig-tp-DBASRMtTT_d" class="text-post-media" style="background: #FFF; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 540px; margin: 1px; min-width: 270px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px); border: 1px solid #00000026;" data-text-post-permalink="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015/post/DBASRMtTT_d" data-text-post-version="0"><div style="padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><div style="display: block; height: 32px; width: 32px; padding-bottom: 20px;"></div><div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; color: #999999; font-weight: 400; padding-bottom: 4px;">Post by @vanmama1015</div><div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; color: #000000; font-weight: 600;">View on Threads</div></div></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.threads.net/embed.js"></script></p><p class="break-words">網民 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015">vanmama1015</a> 在 Threads 上分享了一件有關入境處來電的趣事，表示朋友曾接獲聲稱是入境處職員的電話，對方表示：「X 小姐你好，我係香港入境處&#8230;&#8230;」，未待電話另一方説完，朋友就認為是詐騙電話，隨即收線。</p><p class="break-words">其後對方再次來電，語氣焦急的表示自己的確是香港入境處，懇求朋友不要收線：「你係 X 小姐嗎？我真係香港入境處呀，你唔好收線先&#8230;.」，但朋友亦不予理會，直接收線。</p><p class="break-words">最後該電話第三次來電，以非常焦急的語氣表示自己「真係入境處」，更哀求朋友不要收線：「求下你聽一聽我講先」，然後快速交代問朋友是否正在申請（外籍家庭傭工姓名）來港一事，朋友才警覺的確是真入境處來電。</p><p><a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015">vanmama1015</a> 最後笑指入境處職員比做 cold call（陌生來電銷售）更慘，隨時被「cut 線」拒絕次數更多。下面有網民回應，表示有朋友在入境處工作，真的經常被當成詐騙電話「cut 線」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1-694x210.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="210" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1-694x210.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1.jpg 803w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@cyan421/post/DBAfKozSR9q">Threads</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.immd.gov.hk/publications/a_report_2021/tc/chapter2.html">入境事務處 2021 年年報</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015/post/DBASRMtTT_d">vanmama1015@Threads</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">「微信保險」詐騙電話 Cut 線會打來問原因　連登網民分享對付騙徒新招</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/">Threads 分享真入境處來電慘被 3 次 cut 線，網民回應：經常被當成詐騙電話</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>SpaceX 公開飛船工廠 Starfactory　目標每年生產千艘 Starship 上火星</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=psacex-starfactory</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 07:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SpaceX]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Starship]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268916</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前往我們報道過，Elon Musk 旗下航天製造商和太空運輸公司 SpaceX 10 月 13 日於美國德州成功發射 Starship（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/spacex-starship-5th-launch/fun-tech/">相關報道</a>）。針對 Starship 試飛活動，SpaceX 在發射前夕於 X （前稱 Twitter）發布了一條約 2 分鐘長的影片，介紹其位於美國德州佔地 100 萬平方呎的 Starfactory。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-media-max-width="560"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">The 1-million square foot Starfactory brings many parts of the manufacturing process under one roof for the first time, moving as much system integration work as possible earlier in the build process, with the goal of eventually producing 1,000 Ships a year <a href="https://t.co/vz44XcTTN8">pic.twitter.com/vz44XcTTN8</a></p><p>— SpaceX (@SpaceX) <a href="https://twitter.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 13, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>SpaceX 位於美國德州博卡奇卡（Boca Chica）的 Starfactory 規模龐大，佔地 100 萬平方呎，有效整合飛船製造工序，在同一地點集中多個生產過程，可提前進行系統集成工作。據 SpaceX 帖文表示，Starfactory 目標是年產 1,000 艘飛船。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p>「Starship」是 SpaceX 項目中的重要環節，目標是讓人類實現星際旅行，並且其大規模的生產需要一個高效的製造體系來支援。Elon Musk 曾經表示，Starfactory 僅屬起點，展望未來盼能年產 1,000 艘 Starship，作為邁向火星的基礎。據媒體報道，目前 Starfactory 年產 100 枚火箭，即平均每 3 日可生產一枚火箭。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1007/1007919.htm">快科技</a>、<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/spacex-starship-5th-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SpaceX「筷子」機械臂回收火箭，睇片極似磁吸一樣夾住</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/elon-musk-says-spacex-will-sue-faa-for-regulatory-overreach/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SpaceX 將提告美國聯邦航空總署　Elon Musk 指其過度監管</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/27/louis-vuitton-spacex-rocket-may-happen/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LVMH 總裁與 Elon Mask 會面　曾商討 SpaceX 與 LV 合作</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/">SpaceX 公開飛船工廠 Starfactory　目標每年生產千艘 Starship 上火星</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
